These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, purple, aquamarine
City: liverpool, hannover, san-francisco
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, azalea, zinnia
1. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who likes green##2
3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |   3   |
| Color        | aquamarine | purple | green |
| City         | san-francisco    | liverpool     | hannover  |
| Flower   | zinnia     | azalea     | daffodil  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, ebony, pink
House: victorian, ranch-style, cape-cod
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, superhero, comedy
1. the ranch-style house is the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
3. the person who likes ebony is between the person watching comedy movies and the person who likes green##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |        3        |
| Color   | green    | ebony       | pink             |
| House      | ranch-style  | cape-cod | victorian      |
| Movie-Genre        | crime | superhero    | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-3::.
House: futuristic, modern, victorian
3 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, ferret
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, chestnut, grey
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the dog is the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes green is between the victorian house and the person who likes grey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| House           | victorian    | futuristic   | modern |
| Pet   | chinchilla | dog   | ferret         |
| Color         | chestnut     | green | grey     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-4::.
House: townhouse, victorian, wooden
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, australian, american
3 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, fish
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the fish is between the nigerian and the townhouse house##2
4. the australian is on the right of the victorian house##1
5. the australian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| House   | wooden    | victorian  | townhouse     |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | american   | australian       |
| Pet     | horse | fish | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, sudoku, rock-climbing
There 3 different types of food: garlic, pumpkin, mango
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, italian, australian
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person eating garlic##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the right of the pakistani##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the italian##1
4. the person eating garlic is between the person eating pumpkin and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku   | baking   |
| Food           | pumpkin   | garlic | mango     |
| Nationality     | pakistani   | australian    | italian |

