.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different games are played: go, whist, chess
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, old-henry, dannemann
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, daisy
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the person who growspoppy is between the old-henry-smoker and the person who growsdaisy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |
| Game         | whist   | go | chess |
| Cigar   | bongani | dannemann      | old-henry  |
| Flower   | daisy      | poppy   | zinnia |

