.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, ambient, pop
3 different games are played: domino, bridge, billiard
House: farmhouse, art-deco, colonial
1. the fan techno is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
2. the colonial house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the fan pop is between the farmhouse house and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | pop    | techno |
| Game         | domino   | billiard     | bridge     |
| House     | art-deco | colonial | farmhouse     |

