.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, august, may
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy, poppy
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, mauve, lilac
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who likes azure##2
4. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday         | may | september | august  |
| Flower   | daisy        | poppy        | balloon-flower |
| Color         | mauve         | lilac    | azure   |

