.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-9::.
City: london, hannover, colone
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, dahlia, amaryllis
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, pall-mall, chaman
1. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person traveling to london##2
2. the chaman-smoker is between the siglo-smoker and the person traveling to london##2
3. the person who growsbellflower is in the middle##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| City         | colone | hannover  | london  |
| Flower         | amaryllis    | bellflower | dahlia |
| Cigar   | siglo    | chaman       | pall-mall  |

