.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-10::.
There 3 different types of food: lime, peach, garlic
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, october, july
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, cola
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating lime is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person eating garlic##2
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |
| Food   | peach       | lime         | garlic      |
| Birthday   | october | july       | march |
| Beverage         | cola     | juice | tea |

