.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-11::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, kiwi, onion
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, july, february
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, baccarat, bongani
1. the person eating apple is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person eating onion##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person eating onion and the bongani-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |       3       |
| Food         | onion | apple  | kiwi |
| Birthday   | july      | august       | february          |
| Cigar         | old-henry  | baccarat | bongani        |

