.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, soccer, sailing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, metal, electronic
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, peas, pumpkin
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the fan electronic##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the fan hip-hop is between the fan electronic and the person eating pumpkin##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3       |
| Sport           | soccer   | cycling | sailing |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | hip-hop     | metal       |
| Food   | peas    | raspberry | pumpkin       |

