.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-13::.
City: venice, boston, rome
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, techno, house
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, milk
1. the fan house is between the person drinking milk and the person traveling to rome##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the fan ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| City          | boston      | venice | rome     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | house  | ambient     |
| Beverage         | milk  | hot-chocolate | fanta |

