.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, architect, fisherman
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, indian, indonesian
3 different games are played: backgammon, poker, whist
1. the fisherman is on the left of the architect##1
2. the indian is the architect##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the indian##1
4. the person playing poker is between the indonesian and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |      2      |     3      |
| Job   | fisherman | architect | project-manager   |
| Nationality           | chinese  | indian        | indonesian     |
| Game     | backgammon  | poker   | whist |

