.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-15::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, rat
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, baking, reading
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, turquise, light-blue
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who likes turquise is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the frog##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who likes ivory and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |    3    |
| Pet      | lizard    | rat  | frog |
| Hobby          | reading | baking | photography |
| Color   | light-blue      | turquise | ivory   |

