.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-17::.
3 different games are played: bridge, go, billiard
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, brown, turquise
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, chinese, american
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the american is between the person playing bridge and the person who likes mauve##2
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
4. the person who likes mauve is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3     |
| Game      | bridge | go | billiard     |
| Color           | turquise      | brown | mauve     |
| Nationality   | chinese       | american      | dutch |

