1. the person traveling to boston is the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| City         | new-york | paris | boston |
| Birthday           | october   | april   | november |
| Beverage   | cola     | hot-chocolate | juice   |

