.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-19::.
3 different games are played: poker, billiard, domino
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, badminton, climbing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, january
1. the person playing billiard is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's birthday is in january##2
2. the person playing domino is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person playing billiard##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |      3       |
| Game   | domino | billiard      | poker  |
| Sport      | climbing   | badminton   | golf      |
| Birthday        | november     | august | january |

