.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different games are played: snooker, domino, go
House: wooden, palace, townhouse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, aristoff, bongani
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the person playing snooker is between the palace house and the person playing go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Game    | go     | snooker     | domino |
| House       | townhouse | wooden | palace |
| Cigar   | bongani     | bolivar       | aristoff    |

 